title: Welcome Home To Beckley Townhomes! Make This 2BR Yours Today!
posting_body: ['You’ll find us just off Metz & Beckleymeade Ave., conveniently located in Southern Dallas, right off highways 1-20 & 35E, nearby a variety of dining and entertainment options.', 'Beckley Townhomes offers residents a small town feel while just a short drive to the downtown Dallas.', 'Residents of Beckley Townhomes get the perfect touch of seclusion yet instant access to Dallas & Fort Worth attractions.', 'Our community offers a wide array of amenities including a community clubhouse, outdoor swimming pool, playground area, and 24-hour emergency maintenance.', 'Beckley’s 2 & 3 bedroom townhomes are a perfect place to call home, featuring open & spacious floor plans, ample kitchen cabinet & countertop space, a hallway linen closet and a large private patio space.', 'Reserve your new home at Beckley Townhome’s today before it’s too late!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Picnic & Grilling Areas', '- Convenient On-Site Laundry Facilities', '- On-Site Fitness Center', '- Limited Access Gated Entry System', '- Hallway Linen Closet', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Select homes at Beckley Townhomes participate in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $42,000 | 2 Occupants: $48,000 | 3 Occupants: $54,000 | 4 Occupants: $60,000 | 5 Occupants: $64,800 | 6 Occupants: $69,600.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Wednesday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Beckley Townhomes', '801 Beckleymeade Ave.', 'Dallas, TX, 75232', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'D4tcsxDG']
